reviewText: Great series for a Historical drama. One of my favorites. Product was well worth the money.
Discs and discbox came without damage. Discs ran properly. English subtitle with korean dialogue only. But came without drama's opening theme.

This series was absolutely wonderful, and it kept me glues to the screen for weeks.  Everything about it was terrific, from the acting to the plot, to the acting, to the set productions.  Might be the best Korean drama I ever saw.
